WHO WE ARE
Oakwood Smokehouse is a growing restaurant company established 1998 in Lake County Florida. We are a full service casual Restaurant staffed by professional managers from large restaurant companies.
Fresh cut specialty salads and Oakwood smoked barbecue are only the beginning of a varied menu that has something to offer everyone. Charbroiled burgers, center cut steaks, grilled chicken, fresh soups and baby back ribs are all served from our open kitchen design and will tempt you to try everything.
Our philosophy of keeping operations simple combined with experienced management and a knowledgeable staff gives each one of your visits a consistency you can count on! The casual atmosphere and great prices are the finishing touches to your experience with Oakwood Smokehouse and Grill.
We invite you to visit us.
Oakwood Smokehouse Grill
